SoMat/SIE version 0.02
======================

This is a perl XS interface to libsie, a library for retrieving
data from SoMat SIE data files.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

Note - this version will only compile properly from its home in the
libsie/src directory. Future versions should relax this restriction.

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

  libsie

